pullRequest.body:
This is quite a substantial bump as `Nondet` / `backtrack` / `solve_by_elim` have all moved to Std.


---


Infelicities:
* ~~`Except.emoji` has become `private` in Std, so for now I've just made several copies of it here, at each point of use. leanprover/std4#506 makes it public again.~~
* ~~`MVarId.note` is now in `Std.Tactic.SolveByElim`, so we need to (otherwise unnecessarily) import that. leanprover/std4#507 fixes this.~~
